text: Irina Konstantinovna Mezhonnova (born Irina Malkova, 23 March 1989) is a Russian volleyball player. == Career == She played at the 2014 FIVB Volleyball Women's Club World Championship, 2015 Summer Universiade, 2015 FIVB World Grand Prix, 2015 Montreux Volley Masters, 2016 FIVB Volleyball Women's Club World Championship, and 2017 FIVB Volleyball Women's Club World Championship.
